In this, the LDM 1.0 (including the autoencoder part) is trained with the autoencoder which is trained with sinogram data and then combined together.

This model specifically caters to Sinogram input and Sinogram output.

Please see the repo : https://github.com/CompVis/latent-diffusion and https://github.com/nickyisadog/latent-diffusion-inpainting

**The repo is under development phase**
